 The two sparks soared across earth. Thier bodies haveing beem destroyed for 
cycles thier survival chances shortened. They didnt even know how they 
survived this long. Suddenly in a burst of desperation thier sparks fused. A 
bright light shined. Suddenly a fuzor came forth from the light. It was a 
panther hawk. It came into clear sight to anything near it. it spoke as just 
to make sure to itself it was alive. (in a united voice of two bots) "We are 
savior."
